trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"> </xref> e <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"> </xref> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A> method, and it indicates that the connection process has begun (for example, a user has selected a control and clicked a connect verb), but is not yet completed.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>é gerado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A>método e indica que o processo de conexão foi iniciada (por exemplo, um usuário tem um controle selecionado e clicou em um verbo de conexão), mas ainda não foi concluída.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>

trans-unit.source: The event provides an opportunity to cancel a connection before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: O evento fornece uma oportunidade de cancelar uma conexão antes de ser concluída.

trans-unit.source: If the connection is successfully completed, this event is followed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event.
trans-unit.target: Se a conexão for concluída com êxito, esse evento é seguido de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>evento.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A> method, and it indicates that a user has clicked a disconnect verb, or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A> method has otherwise been called.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>é gerado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A>método e indica que um usuário clicou um verbo de desconexão, ou o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A>método contrário tiver sido chamado.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>

trans-unit.source: The event provides an opportunity to cancel the process of ending a connection before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: O evento fornece uma oportunidade de cancelar o processo de encerrar uma conexão antes de ser concluída.

trans-unit.source: If the connection is ended successfully, this event is followed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event.
trans-unit.target: Se a conexão for concluída com êxito, esse evento é seguido de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>evento.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs class contains information about the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> events.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs contém informações sobre o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>eventos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>

trans-unit.source: It provides access to the Web Parts controls that are being connected or disconnected.
trans-unit.target: Ele fornece acesso aos controles de Web Parts que estão sendo conectados ou desconectados.
